'''''The Belle of Rome''''' ({{lang-it|'''La bella di Roma'''}}) is a [[List of Italian films of 1955|1955]] [[Cinema of Italy|Italian]] [[comedy film]] directed by [[Luigi Comencini]].<ref name="45-59">{{cite book|author1=Roberto Chiti |author2=Roberto Poppi |author3=Enrico Lancia |title=Dizionario del cinema italiano: I film|publisher=Gremese, 1991|isbn=8876055487}}</ref>

